extendedInfo.description: * Please find Installation Instructions Below ** If you wish to support us, you can purchase one of our paid themes. Thank you so much and please remember, we appreciate you! *---Application Name---GO SMS Theme Nation Theme---Description---This is a special thank you for all the people who have supported us and appreciate our work! We hope you enjoy the theme.---What do we offer?---* Custom graphics* Custom backgrounds* Custom icons and chat bubble styles* Professional UI Design* Quality Products* Awesome technical support!---Matching/Similar Themes---If you wish to support us and appreciate our products, you can also check out some of our other themes. Thank you! We appreciate you!---Requirements---This theme will only work with 'GO SMS V3.39 OR ABOVE.You can download 'GO SMS Pro' for FREE from Google Play.---Installation---1. You need the 'GO SMS Pro' application as listed in the 'Requirements' section of this description. Please download that prior to the installation of this theme.2. Wait for the theme to be successfully downloaded and installed.3. Open GO SMS Pro, then navigate through the settings.	Menu-->Themes-->Installed Themes4. Select the theme and then press apply!5. Enjoy your awesome new look!---Support---We can't respond to Google Play comments, so send us an email or contact us via Facebook/Twitter!---Follow Us---Please follow us on Facebook and Twitter for the latest information and updates.---Feedback And Suggestions---If you like the theme, please leave a rating and a comment! If you want to provide some feedback, get in touch with us via email, Facebook or Twitter!---Updates---We update our themes periodically, if there is an urgent need for an update, contact us and let us know! We'll get right on it!---Refunds---You can easily refund the application within 15 minutes of purchase if you are not satisfied. This applies to all Google Play applications.*Thanks for your support and feel free to contact us if you need any assistance whatsoever.*
